* &quot;Showdown!&quot;, MFA Boston, 2016
* &quot;Utagawa&quot;, Brooklyn Museum of Art, 2008 
* &quot;Living for the Moment: Japanese Prints from the Collection of Barbara S. Bowman&quot;, LACMA, 2006

