* &quot;The Love Machine&quot; (Simon &amp; Schuster, 1969) 
* &quot;Once Is Not Enough&quot; (William Morrow, 1973) 
* &quot;Dolores&quot; (William Morrow, 1976) 
* &quot;Yargo&quot; (Bantam, 1979) 

